{"success":true,"result":{"Q_10110634646789-1":{"resources":[],"questions":[{"id":"Q_10110634646789-1","subjectId":101,"knowledgePoints":null,"knowledgePointsNew":[],"testMethods":[{"id":"TM_10100000673226","main":1}],"solutionMethods":[],"resourceIds":null,"resourceIndex":0,"listenUrl":null,"listenName":null,"listenSeconds":0,"exploreSeconds":0,"answersSeconds":0,"paperIds":["P_10100141152530-1"],"books":null,"booksNew":null,"contentTypeId":1010008,"contentType2Id":0,"difficultyInt":3,"description":"阅读课外文章，回答问题","notFitMobile":0,"seconds":540,"complex":1,"nid":null,"lastEditorId":null,"finalAuditorId":null,"roughAuditorIds":null,"content":{"content":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>望远镜的发明</strong></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">300多年前，荷兰莱茵河边的一个小城里，开着一家眼镜店。一天，几个孩子把近视镜片和老花镜片拿出来，在门前玩耍。一个孩子<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">无意</span><span><span style=\"text-decoration: none;\">中把两个镜片叠在一起，一片是近视镜的，一片是老花镜的。当他透过两层镜片看外面的景物时却大喊起来：“奇怪，奇怪，远处的人怎么都到眼前了？远处的房子、树木也都移近了。”别的孩子都围过来争着看，觉得很好玩。</span></span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: none;\">这个消息传出去，让意大利物理学家伽利略听到了，他整整思考了一夜。第二天，他用一个空管子，一头装着凸透镜片，一头装着凹透镜片，拿来看外边的景物，他发现不但景物靠近了，而且</span><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">放大</span><span style=\"text-decoration: none;\">了三倍左右。有好些平常看不见的景物，也都能看见了。</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: none;\">有了这个发现后，伽利略继续研究，六个月以后，他制成了一架</span><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">精致</span><span style=\"text-decoration: none;\">的望远镜。用这架望远镜来看远方的景物，可以移近300倍，放大1000倍。用来观察天空，一向看不见的许多星星，也可以看见了。</span></p>","contentDesc":"","analysis":"","subContents":[{"content":"<p>选出画线词语的近义词。</p><p>无意__$$__</p><p>放大__$$__</p><p>精致__$$__</p>","answers":[{"answer":"1","subAnswers":[],"richTexts":null,"scorePercentage":1,"classification":"","knowledgePoints":null,"knowledgePointsNew":[{"id":"KP_10100077589300","tagId":0,"main":0,"featureIds":[]}],"testMethods":[{"id":"TM_10100000631040","main":1}],"solutionMethods":[],"classificat